{"tid":931820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賣六合彩 香港請大媽 台灣請大ball","createTime":"2018-12-07T09:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T10:00:55.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31de2a62eaf7cb41b29a0336e4abf1145b35331b","tid":931820,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"一名網友去購買台彩刮刮樂時，拍下超兇的女店員，影片引發上千網友蓋樓留言，紛喊「想買彩券了！」<br />\n網友在《臉書》社團「爆廢公社」貼出影片，可見女店員熟絡地幫顧客買彩券和刮刮樂，女店員聲音嬌嗲，且身材「超兇！」女店員還問現場一名「熟客」男性：「你在這邊上班喔？」讓被識破的網友只好羞答「對！附近。」<br />\n<br />\n網友看了影片都快暴動了！「我忽然好想去刮刮樂」、「聲音嗲嗲 ，身材火辣，生意一定很好」，一堆網友更說「害我浪費24h一直重複看」、「播了兩個小時還播不完」、「這啥影片阿...怎麼我都沒看到彩券！可我還是手起刀落手起刀落重看800遍。」還有人說「我根本不在乎有沒有中獎，我只在乎買了彩券能幫助弱勢。能跟我說這在那裡嗎？我要去幫忙弱勢！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181207/1479944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181207%2F1479944&d=J2lDsVeHwS0B9dU1HFKLq26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=664a9276\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181207%2F1479944&h=d6c6c2eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181207/1479944</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181207/640_0f1959c38cec284cc427d32e5be83c6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181207%2F640_0f1959c38cec284cc427d32e5be83c6d.jpg&h=83b66a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4eeeec40cc8629c510d94b545ea87fb7bf5992","tid":931820,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b1963fb65799a18d0112b2b10cb31a0d9b9e77","tid":931820,"uid":72475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"因為香港多大媽 台灣多大波"}]}